content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4815.20 - Identity on bingo cards

State Regulations

No licensed supplier shall sell any type of bingo card
unless there is printed thereon the name, mark or symbol of the printer or
manufacturer which name, mark or symbol has been registered with the
commission. Notes
